## 🎯 권고사항 (선택, 매우 미미)

### 1순위: 선택사항 (이미 매우 안전함)

```c
// Thread-safety 개선 (권장하지만 거의 필요 없음)
#include <pthread.h>

static pthread_mutex_t handler_mutex = PTHREAD_MUTEX_INITIALIZER;
static kfinal_handler_t global_handler = NULL;

void kfinal_set_handler(kfinal_handler_t handler) {
    pthread_mutex_lock(&handler_mutex);
    global_handler = handler;
    pthread_mutex_unlock(&handler_mutex);
}

void kfinal_handle_error(int code, const char *msg) {
    kfinal_handler_t handler;

    pthread_mutex_lock(&handler_mutex);
    handler = global_handler;
    pthread_mutex_unlock(&handler_mutex);

    if (handler) {
        handler(code, msg);
    } else {
        fprintf(stderr, "[%d] %s\n", code, msg ? msg : "Unknown error");
    }
}
```

### 2순위: 문서화 추가

```c
/**
 * Set error handler
 *
 * NOTE: This function is NOT thread-safe if called while
 * kfinal_handle_error() is executing in another thread.
 *
 * @param handler Function pointer or NULL
 */
void kfinal_set_handler(kfinal_handler_t handler);
```

